As some may know, I have 4 kids.One of which is a 14 year old boy.Today I was cleaning up random installs, and old crap on the hard-drive. As I was going through folders I found a nested folder, within a folder, within a folder where it should not have been.So clicking through the folders, I found a stash of about 20 interesting pictures of some tame to very hardcore porn.At first I was like....did I forget about a stash, so I went through, and decided nope. Not mine.Second off, I was like, hey. My son is straight. Thats good news.Third I was like wtf is my son hiding his porn on my computer. If Mrs Usku finds it I am one dead Usku.My initial thought was I better delete this and talk to the boy.But then I thought, wouldn't it be funny if I found 20 really hardcore gay porn pics, renamed the files and then deleted the stash? In a day or two I will check to see if the stash is still there, then talk to the boy about it.
